client/
├── src/
│   ├── assets/          # Images, logos, global styles
│   ├── components/      # Reusable UI (Buttons, Navbar, Card)
│   ├── pages/           # Page views (Home.jsx, AdminDashboard.jsx)
│   ├── services/        # API calls (api.js using fetch or axios)
│   ├── App.jsx          # Main routing & layout wrapper
│   └── main.jsx         # Entry point

folders & pages 
assests folder: images folder, logos folder , global styles page 
components folder: (Reuseable UI) Buttons file, Navbar file, Card file, Header File , Footer file 
pages folder: Home page , about page , measurements page , productdetails and listing page etc
Services folder: Api calls
App.jsx file Main routing & layout wrapper 
main.jsx Entry point 
